                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, R</hi> 258). I took the prisoner—he had a pair of new boots on, which he would not take off, but insisted on keep<lb></lb>ing them—I think he was sober—I searched Carroll, but found nothing on him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> The boy said he would get me a pair, and asked 9<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. for them; I laid half-a-sovereign on the counter; when I said so, the boy denied it. <hi rend="smallCaps">
